{"tid":209201,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離屋冷氣機熱風吹哂入黎","createTime":"2017-04-20T04:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T17:05:49.000Z","uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a9c01c8ff4330a4775b19eca54b5911965c5f0a","tid":209201,"uid":4528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/20/123347_5f3da297729c50971d62fa670b03348d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F20%2F123347_5f3da297729c50971d62fa670b03348d.jpg&h=af7bff8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依幾日，隔離屋晚上就會係廳開冷氣<br />\n咁我本身就唔想開冷氣<br />\n但係佢d熱風廢氣係咁吹入黎<br />\n逼住我關窗，最後都逼住開冷氣<br />\n大家有無反擊良方？"},{"pid":"4d31e9b77dc1f5740bcae12f9f9be4cd34bb8ee2","tid":209201,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"將佢部冷氣調轉裝"},{"pid":"cd31b0b1138ed1425dd9f5c613cc399d2c5e564a","tid":209201,"uid":33655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"試下係出面裝多部冷氣"},{"pid":"02f275d739e3f803fbe5681c513a69f567fff49f","tid":209201,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"千萬唔好係佢個散熱痴塊海棉上去, 唔係好易壞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d8e065fe581b2f1b40b0b5bea227f515a9e5cb","tid":209201,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"戇鳩邊關事<br />\n散熱點會咁吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1572adfa344bdb57bfa7607c4f4a1942a385ac","tid":209201,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:52:16.000Z","msg":"幫佢裝風喉向其他方向吹"},{"pid":"eca298c5e0f1072a6868d4498e40a644667835b9","tid":209201,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將佢部冷氣調轉裝</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/asset